249
00:12:12,290 --> 00:12:14,260
Flower

Capital

250
00:12:14,260 --> 00:12:18,970
Kozuki Sukiyaki

(Oden's Father)

Shogun of Wano

251
00:12:14,630 --> 00:12:17,470
Oden, why the sudden visit?

252
00:12:17,470 --> 00:12:18,970
And without your retainers.

253
00:12:18,970 --> 00:12:21,600
Could you let this man stay here?

254
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:24,600
He is a hard worker
and can even prepare medicine.

255
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:26,850
He is like a younger brother to me.

256
00:12:27,310 --> 00:12:29,190
My name is Orochi.

257
00:12:32,060 --> 00:12:35,360
Everyone, please look after Orochi!

258
00:12:35,860 --> 00:12:37,650
Very well, my lord!

259
00:12:47,540 --> 00:12:50,040
Shogun Sukiyaki!

260
00:12:50,500 --> 00:12:53,210
I've finally made it this far!

261
00:12:54,300 --> 00:13:00,260
Back to

Where We

Started

262
00:13:05,890 --> 00:13:08,770
Lord Sukiyaki! Stay with us!

263
00:13:08,770 --> 00:13:10,140
Lord Sukiyaki!

264
00:13:10,140 --> 00:13:11,520
Lord Sukiyaki!

265
00:13:12,770 --> 00:13:15,480
Should anything befall me...

266
00:13:15,900 --> 00:13:17,610
I'm counting on you, Orochi!

267
00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:22,990
